NUMBER 2310
NAME Garump Mansion, porch
CHANNEL 181
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
The front porch of the mansion is most curious, mainly because you cannot
see the property the mansion is built on. There is only a field of black night
and white, sparkling stars out there, as though the night sky were below you.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 0 943 VAL2=2311

;
