NUMBER 2311
NAME Garump Mansion, entrance
REGION 181
CHANNEL 181
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS

*DESCRIPTION_START
A double row of torches marks the sides of a long, narrow corridor,
stretching north out of sight. Its ceiling, floor and walls are all composed
of the same pinkish-gray stone as the door, a substance that looks soft but
isn't. You note that there is no bar or lock on the door- nor a handle.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 0 946 ADJ1=464 ADJ2=312 VAL2=2310

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The door's hinges are on the other side, and it has no handle or locking
mechanism. From this side, it might as well be a part of the wall when it's
closed.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 0
        IFITEM 0 OPEN
                GMMSG %N walked out the door, Dan. They have made it out.
        ENDIF
ENDIF

