                ECHO PLAYER The gargoyle statue leers towards the chandelier and the table below it,
                ECHO PLAYER as though criticizing the work of the craftsmen who created them. Its own
                ECHO PLAYER form is incredibly lifelike, but does not move like a true, summoned
                ECHO PLAYER gargoyle would. Eyes without pupils and a beaklike nose are deepset above
                ECHO PLAYER each gaping, fanged mouth.
                IFVAR ITEMVAL2 = 334
                        ECHO PLAYER Behind the third statue you see a metal plate set into the wall.
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF

