NUMBER 2319
NAME Garump Mansion, secret room
REGION 181
CHANNEL 181
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in a secret room, sealed off from the main corridors of the house
and expertly concealed. There are no decorations here, only a stark utility
indicating that the master decorator was not consulted for its design. A
spiral stairway leads up at the south end of the room, while the north
wall has a simple lever of copper metal attatched to a hinge mechanism.
*DESCRIPTION_END

