ITEM 1 86
ITEM 2 86
ITEM 3 1305
EXTEND 3 which lies against the wall, torn open
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The couch was once a proud, leatherbacked member of its furniturial species. Now, alas, cruel fate has transpired to tear it open and show off its hidden desires, its springs and its frame to the world. A silent tear begins to well in your eye as you contemplate this upholstered tragedy, until you realize how silly that is and blink it away.
*DESCRIPTION_END

